  <brief_title>Effect of Hepatic Impairment on LDE225..</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I, Open Label, Multi-center, Single Dose Study to Evaluate the Pharmacokinetics of LDE225 in Healthy Subjects With Normal Hepatic Function and Subjects With Impaired Hepatic Function.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
